title: MOMOLAND's Yeonwoo Returns After Recovering From Injury | Soompi
text:
Display.Sharethrough.Soompi.1x1 
MOMOLAND is complete once again! 
On February 27, Yeonwoo announced her recovery and return to the group’s activities through a V Live broadcast. 
In the video, the rest of the MOMOLAND members were on a trip to Everland in Yongin city. They then introduced Yeonwoo as a surprise guest, and she cheered, “I’m back!” 
In December, Yeonwoo temporarily withdrew from the group’s activities to receive treatment for injuries on her back and shoulder. 
Dublekick Company stated, “Thanks to the focus on her treatment, Yeonwoo’s health has improved a lot and she has returned to the team. We thank everyone for their concern.” 
Meanwhile, with their complete member lineup, MOMOLAND has kicked off preparations for their new album.
